.TH CAP-WARN-CONFIGURE 8 "June 2026" "cap-alert 1.0.4" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
cap-alert-configure \- interactive CAP-Alert setup wizard
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cap-alert-configure
.SH DESCRIPTION
Runs the Debian debconf wizard for CAP-Alert. Writes /etc/cap-alert/config.php
and installs the systemd timer interval.
.PP
Re-running the wizard updates wizard-owned settings and preserves manually
edited keys such as alert hooks, playback window, and advanced tuning.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR cap-alert (8)
